text:
Hope you all are looking forward to class tonight! Tonight we are gonna be deciding on a team name and covering all sorts of topics. From what I see in the group channel, it looks like the names that are currently in the air are...
-J.R Buddies
-Dream Team
-CR double M

We also need to decide on the project you will be building. Looking forward to your decisions!
